  <div class="info-box">Use this form to draft your research design step by step. The builder follows the structure recommended by Baglione (2020) and George & Bennett (2005): start with a puzzle, articulate a question, choose your epistemological stance, identify your theory, select methods, and justify your cases. When you're done, the tool generates a formatted memo you can share with your supervisor or peers.</div>
