  <div class="form-group"><label>5. Theoretical Framework</label><textarea id="bd-theory" placeholder="Which IR theory or theoretical tradition informs your analysis? (e.g., offensive realism, constructivism, feminist IR, liberal institutionalism). How does it help frame your question?"></textarea></div>
  <div class="form-group"><label>6. Hypothesis / Argument</label><textarea id="bd-hyp" placeholder="If positivist: state your hypothesis and its observable implications. If interpretivist/critical: state your central argument or analytical proposition."></textarea></div>
